# Cloudflare WAF Bypass

Techniques for bypassing Cloudflare Web Application Firewall.

## Description

Cloudflare WAF uses signature-based and behavioral analysis to block
malicious requests. These techniques focus on payload obfuscation.

## Techniques

- Unicode normalization bypass
- Chunked transfer encoding
- Header manipulation

## Indicators

Cloudflare returns specific headers: `cf-ray`, `server: cloudflare`.
